  <ethicsAndSummary>
    <summary>70% of children experience significant pre-operative anxiety and their anxiety levels peak at the time of mask induction. This study aims to familiarise children with the anaesthesia face mask prior to induction of anaesthesia with a cheap and readily available intervention: a playful, song based video that children will enjoy watching.</summary>
